{"tid":2071611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方拒評黎智英跟蹤者身份","createTime":"2020-06-20T03:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T02:39:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"38a1c48d9bf64c6b2d517cf59052b5b263c49e99","tid":2071611,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/4DNI2V5XHC7U34ZSCVHM5YN6N4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2F4DNI2V5XHC7U34ZSCVHM5YN6N4%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=1c51b508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2F4DNI2V5XHC7U34ZSCVHM5YN6N4%2F&h=a80d25fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/4DNI2V5XHC7U34ZSCVHM5YN6N4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警方拒評黎智英跟蹤者身份<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】白色恐怖繼續籠罩香港，壹傳媒創辦人黎智英連續四日被。。。。。續封口拒答，有人更囂張說：「使乜答你啫！」<br />\n<br />\n本周二起，兩輛黑色及白色的七人車一直跟蹤黎智英的座駕，至昨日已是第四日。。。。。。男子更用手機反拍記者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jKO0Kn2NHcEL7e5keXbaeX7ClPI=/802x447/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W56G4JT7XAQLRQY6TDYF6WW3UA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjKO0Kn2NHcEL7e5keXbaeX7ClPI%3D%2F802x447%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW56G4JT7XAQLRQY6TDYF6WW3UA.jpg&h=4a45a8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n七人車在蘋果大樓外守候，後座乘客掩面避開鏡頭。周鴻熙攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一人與警員同名<br />\n<br />\n早上近8時，黎智英由司機接載離開寓所，返回將軍澳工業邨蘋果日報大樓，兩輛七人車一直尾隨，黎的座駕駛入大樓後，兩車停在大樓外。記者上前問他們尾隨目的，各人低頭掩面避開鏡頭。黑色車前座男子更拍拍身旁的司機，示意駕車離開。記者繼續追問，司機則回應：「使乜答你啫！」兩車一度駛離，但在附近繞圈後又折返停泊。<br />\n<br />\n日前該白色七人車上有名男子李X業，他自稱為「真傳媒服務公司」資料搜集員，本報揭發他與一名資深警員同名同姓。記者前日向警方求證李X業身份，並要求警方澄清與跟蹤是否有關，警方昨終回覆，但指「不評論個別個案」，又稱市民如發現有罪案發生，可以報警。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BOWVT5ISCCTMKSYKPJ6CCSERYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBOWVT5ISCCTMKSYKPJ6CCSERYE.jpg&h=6696a969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑色車尾隨黎智英座駕駛入將軍澳工業邨。"},{"pid":"960583436c3c8cd0b1c4765288a15134d47bd6d2","tid":2071611,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f324230b10bad3c948e2dc84f0fd9912760725e","tid":2071611,"uid":179718,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"根本就狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ffcbd45870658c754dd324a064b351c59c2d84","tid":2071611,"uid":227271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"支那国安定港狗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a62e9234a1344f2e68e4c817f044343af5fe9f","tid":2071611,"uid":322638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"低質答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5d0618aa714f1a40b856b0a11663d5de2b65eb","tid":2071611,"uid":7369,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"34ffcbd45870658c754dd324a064b351c59c2d84","tid":2071611,"uid":227271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"支那国安定港狗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:49:51.000Z","msg":"似係退休狗"},{"pid":"5bb3fffff889d540dd0bcf1923b51e6966d9f836","tid":2071611,"uid":31738,"like":